Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: plm, pco, panelvar, pvars, vars, stats
Suggests: readxl, knitr, rmarkdown
